 was serving guests..I have found many times that Indian staff are more laid back in serving guests whereas Filipino staff are very attentive and keen to please..As someone who has cruised on a number of times I have to say that for service you just cant beat it and maybe it has spoiled me.Whatever your looking to achieve by coming to this hotel I am certain it could be acheived by going somewhere else	
